Package fr.gouv.vitam.metadata.core

package fr.gouv.vitam.metadata.core
Provides

  • core interface and implementation for the Metadata module
  • a factory class to get access to MongoDB
  • a factory class to get access to ElasticSearch
  • a factory class in order to use a DbRequest object
